<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Car AC Components - SmartAC</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/aos@next/dist/aos.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/theme-toggle.css">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#000000">
    <style>
        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            background-color: var(--body-bg);
            color: var(--text-color);
        }
        .dashboard-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
            color: white;
            padding: 2.5rem 0;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .dashboard-header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50px;
            right: -50px;
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .dashboard-header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -80px;
            left: -80px;
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .section-divider {
            height: 4px;
            width: 60px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: var(--footer-bg);
            color: var(--footer-text);
            padding: 3rem 0 1.5rem;
            margin-top: auto;
        }
        .footer-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        /* Mobile optimizations */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            body {
                -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
                touch-action: manipulation;
            }
            
            .container {
                padding-left: 15px;
                padding-right: 15px;
            }
            
            .display-4 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .lead {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            
            .model-controls {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            
            .model-controls button {
                margin: 5px !important;
            }
            
            #viewAR {
                width: 100%;
                margin-top: 10px !important;
            }
            
            .row > div {
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="animate__animated animate__fadeIn" style="background-color: #121212; color: #ffffff;">
    <div class="container-fluid p-0 d-flex flex-column min-vh-100">
        <%- include('../partials/teacher-header', {user: user, activePage: 'components'}) %>

    <section class="hero-section py-5 text-center d-flex align-items-center" style="background-color: var(--bs-dark); color: var(--bs-white);">
        <div class="container py-5 mt-5">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000">
                    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-3" style="color: var(--bs-white);">Car AC <span class="text-primary">Components</span></h1>
                    <div class="section-divider mb-4 mx-auto"></div>
                    <p class="lead mb-5" style="color: var(--bs-light);">Explore the components of a car air conditioning system in 3D</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container py-5 ">
        <div class="row mb-5">
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="card shadow-sm" style="border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; background-color: #1a1a1a; color: #ffffff;">
                    <div class="card-body p-4">
                        <div class="model-container rounded-4 overflow-hidden mb-4" id="completeSystemContainer" style="border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-offset="200" data-aos-once="true">
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center h-100" style="min-height: 400px;">
                                <model-viewer src="/models/normal.glb" 
                                    alt="3D model of AC system" 
                                    auto-rotate 
                                    camera-controls 
                                    shadow-intensity="1" 
                                    style="width: 100%; height: 400px; opacity: 0;" 
                                    class="aos-animate" 
                                    id="acSystemModel">
                                </model-viewer>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="model-controls p-4 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center bg-dark rounded-4 gap-3">
                            <button class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill px-4 py-2 shadow-sm" id="rotateLeft"><i class="bi bi-arrow-counterclockwise me-1"></i></button>
                            <button class="btn btn-info rounded-pill px-4 py-2 shadow-sm" id="resetView"><i class="bi bi-aspect-ratio me-1"></i></button>
                            <button class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill px-4 py-2 shadow-sm" id="rotateRight"><i class="bi bi-arrow-clockwise me-1"></i></button>
                            <button class="btn btn-lg rounded-pill px-5 py-3 ms-4 ar-button shadow" id="viewAR" data-model="normal.glb" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF5F6D, #FFC371); color: white; border: none; font-weight: bold;"><i class="bi bi-phone me-2"></i></button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-12 text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800">
                <h2 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-3">Components of Car AC</h2>
                <div class="section-divider mb-4 mx-auto"></div>
                <p class="lead mb-5">Components Asas Aircon kenderaan.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Core Components Section -->
        <div class="row g-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800" data-aos-delay="100">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm component-card" style="background-color: #1a1a1a; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 20px;">
                    <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                        <h3 class="card-title text-center fw-bold fs-5 mb-3">1. Pemampat (Compressor)</h3>
                        <p class="card-text text-center mb-4">Menyedut bahan pendingin dari penyejat dalam bentuk wap bersuhu dan bertekanan rendah. Memampatkan bahan pendingin berbentuk wap ke suhu bertekanan tinggi.</p>
                        <div class="mt-auto text-center">
                            <a href="/teacher/component/compressor" class="btn btn-primary px-4">View</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800" data-aos-delay="100">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm component-card" style="background-color: #1a1a1a; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 20px;">
                    <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                        <h3 class="card-title text-center fw-bold fs-5 mb-3">2. Pemeluwap (Condenser)</h3>
                        <p class="card-text text-center mb-4">Memerangkap dan menyingkirkan haba yang dibawa oleh bahan pendingin. Menyejukkan bahan pendingin bersuhu dan bertekanan tinggi menggunakan aliran udara.</p>
                        <div class="mt-auto text-center">
                            <a href="/teacher/component/condenser" class="btn btn-primary px-4">View</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800" data-aos-delay="100">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm component-card" style="background-color: #1a1a1a; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 20px;">
                    <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                        <h3 class="card-title text-center fw-bold fs-5 mb-3">3. Injap Pengembangan Termostatik (TXV)</h3>
                        <p class="card-text text-center mb-4">Menurunkan suhu dan tekanan bahan pendingin bentuk cecair daripada suhu bertekanan tinggi ke suhu bertekanan rendah. Mengawal kadar aliran bahan pendingin.</p>
                        <div class="mt-auto text-center">
                            <a href="/teacher/component/txv" class="btn btn-primary px-4">View</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800" data-aos-delay="100">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm component-card" style="background-color: #1a1a1a; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 20px;">
                    <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                        <h3 class="card-title text-center fw-bold fs-5 mb-3">4. Gegelung Penyejuk (Penyejat)</h3>
                        <p class="card-text text-center mb-4">Memerangkap haba dan bahan pendingin menyerap haba daripada ruang yang hendak disejukkan. Menukarkan bentuk bahan pendingin daripada bentuk cecair kepada bentuk wap.</p>
                        <div class="mt-auto text-center">
                            <a href="/teacher/component/cooling-coil" class="btn btn-primary px-4">View</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800" data-aos-delay="100">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm component-card" style="background-color: #1a1a1a; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 20px;">
                    <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                        <h3 class="card-title text-center fw-bold fs-5 mb-3">5. Penapis Pengering (Receiver Drier)</h3>
                        <p class="card-text text-center mb-4">Menapis kotoran dan menyerap kelembapan daripada bahan pendingin sebelum ia kembali ke injap pengembangan termostatik.</p>
                        <div class="mt-auto text-center">
                            <a href="/teacher/component/receiver-drier" class="btn btn-primary px-4">View</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800" data-aos-delay="100">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm component-card" style="background-color: #1a1a1a; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 20px;">
                    <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                        <h3 class="card-title text-center fw-bold fs-5 mb-3">6. Kaca Pemerhati (Sight Glass)</h3>
                        <p class="card-text text-center mb-4">Membolehkan pemeriksaan visual untuk mengesan kuantiti (jumlah) bahan pendingin sama ada cukup atau kurang dalam sistem.</p>
                        <div class="mt-auto text-center">
                            <a href="/teacher/component/sight-glass" class="btn btn-primary px-4">View</a>                       </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800" data-aos-delay="100">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm component-card" style="background-color: #1a1a1a; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 20px;">
                    <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                        <h3 class="card-title text-center fw-bold fs-5 mb-3">7. Suis Tekanan (Pressure Switch)</h3>
                        <p class="card-text text-center mb-4">Memutuskan aliran elektrik sistem apabila tekanan terlalu tinggi atau terlalu rendah untuk mengelakkan kerosakan pemampat dan memastikan keselamatan.</p>
                        <div class="mt-auto text-center">
                            <a href="/teacher/component/pressure-switch" class="btn btn-primary px-4">View</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        
        
